---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Rates &amp; Turnaround"
  description="Lynden Howells provides competitive proofreading rates based on document complexity, with typical turnaround of 24–48 hours. Urgent work available."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Rates &amp; Turnaround</h1>
      <p class="page-header__sub">Transparent pricing based on the work involved</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h2>How I charge</h2>
      <hr class="gold-rule" />
      <p>
        My rates are hourly and vary based on the complexity and technical difficulty
        of the document. There is no single "standard" rate — a straightforward newsletter
        and a highly technical pharmaceutical prescribing information document are
        very different assignments that require different levels of care and expertise.
      </p>
      <p>
        Before I take on any job, I ask to see a sample of the work. This is so I can
        give you an accurate quote and confirm I can meet your deadline. I won't quote
        sight unseen, and it protects both of us from difficult conversations later.
      </p>

      <h2>Turnaround times</h2>
      <hr class="gold-rule" />

      <div class="cards" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Standard</h3>
          <p>
            A typical 20-page A4 document (such as a small annual report with photos
            and graphics) is usually returned within <strong>24–48 hours</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Urgent</h3>
          <p>
            Rush jobs are available. An urgent rate is agreed in advance before
            I begin work, so there are no surprises on either side.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>How to get a quote</h2>
      <hr class="gold-rule" />
      <p>
        Getting a quote is straightforward:
      </p>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Send me a sample of your document (or the full document if it's ready).</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Tell me your deadline and any specific requirements.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">I'll come back to you promptly with a quote and a confirmed timeframe.</li>
      </ol>

      <div class="highlight-box">
        <p style="margin:0;">
          I'm happy to discuss your project informally before committing to anything.
          Just get in touch and we'll take it from there.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-2"><a href="/contact" class="btn">Request a Quote</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
